<div id="pf24" class="pf w4 h2" data-page-no="24"><div class="pc pc24 w4 h2"><div class="t m3f0 x44 h1e y513 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Creation, incarnation and re-creation, the Godhead is at work, and always </div><div class="t m41 x44 h1e y514 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Spirit brings God&apos;s objective to its goal. </div><div class="t m277 x49 h1d y515 ff6 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What other special role is filled by the Holy Spirit? 2 Peter 1:20, 21. </div><div class="t m20e x49 h1e y516 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Not only did the Holy Spirit inspire the prophets in producing the Scrip-</div><div class="t m35c x44 h1e y26c ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tures but He also has helped people through the ages understand what was </div><div class="t m3f1 x44 h1e y26d ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">written. Through His ministry the Scriptures come alive, making Christ real </div><div class="t m35c x44 h1e y26e ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to us today, softening our hearts to the Saviour, and enabling us to live for </div><div class="t m3ad x44 h1e y26f ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Him. </div><div class="t m234 x44 h1d y52 ff6 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SEARCH AND LEARN: What other indications are given of the </div><div class="t m201 x19 h1d y517 ff6 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Spirit&apos;s ministry in Old Testament times? </div><div class="t m227 x49 h1e y518 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m3f2 x45 h1e y518 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Gen 61 </div><div class="t m8b x39 h1e y492 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m229 xaa h1e y492 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div><div class="t m22a x49 h1e y519 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m3f3 x45 h1e y519 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Ex. 31</div><div class="t m234 x67 h1e y519 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">.</div><div class="t m1e5 x69 h1e y519 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3 </div><div class="t m8b x39 h1e y519 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m229 xaa h1e y519 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div><div class="t m22c x49 h1e y494 f